{"tid":1168562,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同個男仔約過一次 之後有日日吹水","createTime":"2019-05-23T18:14:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T10:51:46.000Z","uid":2213,"like":8,"dislike":103,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"2bfee6f0e5f79162647be2655550d0afca42eeb1","tid":1168562,"uid":2213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T18:14:43.000Z","msg":"同個男仔有約過出去食過次飯<br />\n個日個氣氛都唔錯<br />\n之後都有日日message 但都只係閒計 我都有問佢得唔得閒再約<br />\n佢都會話好忙 （個排佢真係忙）<br />\n之後傾計講開有套戲話好正 會想再睇<br />\n我就主動約佢 但係佢就話好忙 但係會想再睇<br />\n最近我見佢好似無咁忙 就問佢最近點<br />\n佢就話無野搞 但係當我問佢忙完啦？ 佢就話其實都唔係 最近都揾緊野做 然後一直圍繞揾野做呢個話題傾落去 <br />\n咁其實我係咪冇機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地只係普通朋友 我應唔應該再主動d約佢定放棄"},{"pid":"4888c535d6a7d87d3d85e2d6b3d64750c2221eef","tid":1168562,"uid":201604,"like":121,"dislike":2,"score":119,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T18:15:36.000Z","msg":"佢嬲你唔畀佢含"},{"pid":"beffea76890dcf8f1c6a9178f163c76fc277c814","tid":1168562,"uid":2213,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4888c535d6a7d87d3d85e2d6b3d64750c2221eef","tid":1168562,"uid":201604,"like":121,"dislike":2,"score":119,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T18:15:36.000Z","msg":"佢嬲你唔畀佢含"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T18:17:28.000Z","msg":"應該唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d93052cb74dcc10bbb39e823a1acdff0520258","tid":1168562,"uid":221621,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T18:17:47.000Z","msg":"你試下唔搵佢一排<br />\n睇下佢會唔搵翻你"},{"pid":"bc6ebcea9ba6808e21173ac481c204372e390b8f","tid":1168562,"uid":102961,"like":147,"dislike":0,"score":147,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T18:18:25.000Z","msg":"你咁主動 佢都唔so你 知咩事啦"},{"pid":"fb3709fd3ed2c40d136d9d9d8b0412849272751d","tid":1168562,"uid":223816,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T18:18:44.000Z","msg":"你地會唔會傾d交心既野"},{"pid":"b3b48fb824c0bb617a6e95f71b25ef394e980199","tid":1168562,"uid":2213,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"bc6